Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.96,0:00:18.83,Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,Kokoâ€”
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.20,0:00:19.33,Overlap,Yae,0,0,0,,Kokona{**-san}!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.18,0:00:23.86,Default,Yae,0,0,0,,Let's make this a great opening night!
