Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.80,0:00:33.76,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.46,0:00:36.88,Default,Yae (Genie),0,0,0,,Master...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.15,0:00:39.84,Default,Yae (Genie),0,0,0,,Trust me!
