Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.45,0:04:14.09,Default,Audience 1,0,0,0,,Hey, let's go buy some merch!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.09,0:04:15.97,Default,Audience 2,0,0,0,,Great idea! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.34,0:04:21.44,Default,Audience 1,0,0,0,,What?! Yae{**-chan}'s photos are all sold out?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.69,0:04:23.69,Default,Staff,0,0,0,,We're terribly sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.22,0:04:30.24,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.69,0:04:31.73,Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,Kokona.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.85,0:04:35.55,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,Oh, Shizuka{**-chan}. What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.41,0:04:39.30,Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,Kokona, can we talk for a bit?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.30,0:04:43.41,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,Sorry! I promised Yae{**-chan} I'd \Npractice some songs with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.70,0:04:46.19,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,But tell me what you thought \Nof the show later!
