Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.75,0:07:13.13,Default,Kathrina,0,0,0,,So Arabian.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.13,0:07:15.86,Default,Panda,0,0,0,,They're all gifts from Sassu's fans.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.06,0:07:20.91,Default,Kathrina,0,0,0,,Uh... Even that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.91,0:07:22.87,Default,Sasuga,0,0,0,,Actually, I bought this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.78,0:07:24.98,Default,Kathrina,0,0,0,,But why?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.77,0:07:27.61,Default,Panda,0,0,0,,You know...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.30,0:07:30.65,Default,Panda,0,0,0,,We've been selling out each show.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.65,0:07:33.41,Default,Panda,0,0,0,,There's been nothing but \Nrave reviews from the audience.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.41,0:07:35.69,Default,Panda,0,0,0,,The critics have nothing but praise.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.69,0:07:39.01,Default,Panda,0,0,0,,And the day that Niizumacchi\Nbecomes a Dai Star draws near.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.31,0:07:43.28,Default,Panda,0,0,0,,But is this {\i1}Arabian Nights{\i0} \Nrun really okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.64,0:07:46.07,Default,Kathrina,0,0,0,,If you're hinting at something, \Njust spit it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.33,0:07:51.42,Default,Panda,0,0,0,,Koko{**-chan}'s performance.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.42,0:07:55.08,Default,Panda,0,0,0,,It's been solely for Niizumacchi, hasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.08,0:07:58.47,Default,Sasuga,0,0,0,,Yeah. She's just being the foil.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.47,0:08:00.58,Default,Panda,0,0,0,,Is that how a star {\i1}should{\i0} be?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.58,0:08:03.32,Default,Panda,0,0,0,,Usually, supporting roles\N make the {\i1}lead{\i0} shine!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.56,0:08:04.73,Default,Kathrina,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.73,0:08:08.09,Default,Kathrina,0,0,0,,The one who should be carrying \Nthe story isn't doing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.38,0:08:12.27,Default,Sasuga,0,0,0,,But Kokona's performance is \Ndefinitely getting better.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.27,0:08:13.67,Default,Panda,0,0,0,,Exactly!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.67,0:08:16.29,Default,Panda,0,0,0,,That's what's bugging me even more!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.29,0:08:18.80,Default,Panda,0,0,0,,I'm getting dark circles\Nfrom losing sleep over it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.80,0:08:20.92,Default,Sasuga,0,0,0,,You're like a real panda. It's cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.25,0:08:32.62,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,Well? How was today's show?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.80,0:08:36.03,Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,I felt nothing from your performance.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.03,0:08:36.64,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.32,0:08:41.75,Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,I couldn't understand the Aladdin\N you were trying to play at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.37,0:08:47.59,Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,Because you're only performing for Yae{**-chan}.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.57,0:08:50.20,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,Th-That's not...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.20,0:08:51.76,Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,Can you really deny it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.91,0:08:57.71,Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,The play's gotten great reviews, \Nand the audience seems satisfied.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.34,0:09:03.89,Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,But right now, your performance is bland, \Nlike you're trying to stay out of Yae{**-chan}'s way.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.34,0:09:09.53,Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,This is our first lead role.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.53,0:09:13.13,Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,At this rate, you'll just \Nend up Yae{**-chan}'s foil.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.13,0:09:15.03,Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,You understand that, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.28,0:09:17.55,Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,So let's try this together one more timeâ€”
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.55,0:09:18.27,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.27,0:09:21.79,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,I have another show tomorrow,\Nso I'm gonna go rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.86,0:09:28.19,Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,Kokona...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.43,0:09:38.70,Default,Kokona (Aladdin),0,0,0,,You said you'd grant me \Nany wish, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.70,0:09:39.59,Default,Niizuma (Genie),0,0,0,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.59,0:09:42.96,Default,Niizuma (Genie),0,0,0,,As long as you're the master of the lamp,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.96,0:09:46.06,Default,Niizuma (Genie),0,0,0,,I'll grant you as many wishes as you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.29,0:09:52.69,Default,Niizuma (Genie),0,0,0,,Oh! But I can't bring anyone back \Nfrom the dead or control anyone's mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.69,0:09:56.08,Default,Kokona (Aladdin),0,0,0,,But it can be anything else?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.08,0:09:59.02,Default,Niizuma (Genie),0,0,0,,Sure can! I'll grant you any wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.02,0:10:01.86,Default,Niizuma (Genie),0,0,0,,I am the Genie of the Lamp, after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.56,0:10:08.59,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm sorry, Shizuka{**-chan},\Nbut I'm having so much fun right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.06,0:10:13.96,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,{\i1}I mean... I'm on the stage I always \Ndreamed of, performing with Yae{**-chan}!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.78,0:10:16.02,Default,Kokona (Aladdin),0,0,0,,Genie?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.02,0:10:18.83,Default,Niizuma (Genie),0,0,0,,Hey! You don't believe me, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.19,0:10:21.26,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,{\i1}I don't care if I'm the foil.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.26,0:10:26.50,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,{\i1}As long as this play is a success... \NAs long as the audience is happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.50,0:10:27.23,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.64,0:10:34.51,Default,Kokona (Aladdin),0,0,0,,I'm not so sure about a genie \Nlooking like you do...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.51,0:10:37.48,Default,Yae (Genie),0,0,0,,Well, you can't judge a genie by its cover!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.97,0:10:45.57,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,{\i1}They're not looking at me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.23,0:10:58.12,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,{\i1}No one is looking at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.28,0:11:05.01,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,{\pos(964.368,386.907)\org(964.368,386.907)\fscy99.662\frx-1.67\fnArial\fs108\b1\xbord0\ybord0\c&H8A62FD&\3c&HFFFFFF&\fad(1200,1)}S{\c&HF9AA06&}t{\c&H30C2FF&}e{\c&H8A62FD&}l{\c&HF9AA06&}l{\c&H30C2FF&}a {\c&H8A62FD&}o{\c&HF9AA06&}f{\c&H30C2FF&} t{\c&H8A62FD&}h{\c&HF9AA06&}e {\c&H30C2FF&}T{\c&H8A62FD&}h{\c&HF9AA06&}e{\c&H30C2FF&}a{\c&H8A62FD&}t{\c&HF9AA06&}e{\c&H30C2FF&}r{\c&H8A62FD&}:
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.13,0:11:14.53,Default,Panda,0,0,0,,Koko{**-chan}?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.54,0:11:29.43,Default,Niizuma (Genie),0,0,0,,Every human who's ever met me \Ngets stunned into silence,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.43,0:11:32.86,Default,Niizuma (Genie),0,0,0,,but I guess it took you a bit\N longer to get there!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.41,0:11:36.11,Default,Niizuma,0,0,0,,The stage is going to go dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.11,0:11:37.71,Default,Niizuma,0,0,0,,Let's regroup from there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.16,0:11:43.12,Default,Niizuma (Genie),0,0,0,,All right! Let's try this \Nagain and have some fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.97,0:11:46.32,Default,Panda,0,0,0,,She's so good.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.32,0:11:48.87,Default,Panda,0,0,0,,She managed to turn Koko{**-chan}'s \Nmistake into a laugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.87,0:11:50.88,Default,Kathrina,0,0,0,,Don't make us sweat like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.43,0:12:05.90,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,{\i1}I didn't notice because I've been so swept \Nup in my performance since the first day.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.36,0:12:10.53,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,{\i1}All this cheering and applause is for...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.73,0:12:18.17,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.17,0:12:21.12,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,I can't believe I forgot my line \Nafter we rehearsed so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.12,0:12:22.77,Default,Niizuma,0,0,0,,It's perfectly fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.14,0:12:26.63,Default,Niizuma,0,0,0,,I'll make sure to cover for you, \Nno matter what happens!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.07,0:12:30.64,Default,Niizuma,0,0,0,,Let's put it behind us and \Nprepare for the next show.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.41,0:12:32.33,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.50,0:12:36.60,Default,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,Kokona.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.71,0:12:39.00,Default,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,Can I have a word with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.78,0:12:48.76,Default,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,You couldn't concentrate at \Nall during that performance.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.24,0:12:50.68,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.77,0:12:58.66,Default,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,There's no show tomorrow,\Nso make sure you get plenty of rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.25,0:13:02.40,Default,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,Resting is also part of your job.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.45,0:13:04.40,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.43,0:13:11.43,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,{\an8\fnArial\b1\c&H5044C1&\3c&HEFEFEF&\4c&HEFEFEF&}BATH
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.85,0:13:16.73,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,What am I supposed to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.91,0:13:20.94,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,Shizuka{**-chan}, what would you...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.70,0:13:24.45,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,Huh? Shizuka{**-chan}?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.16,0:13:32.27,Default,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.37,0:13:34.66,Default,Panda,0,0,0,,Pardon me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.03,0:13:38.79,Default,Panda,0,0,0,,Hiiragi{**-san}, do you have a moment?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.79,0:13:39.47,Default,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.39,0:13:45.83,Default,Panda,0,0,0,,Do you think this production of\N{\i1}Arabian Nights{\i0} is really benefiting SIRIUS?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.39,0:13:47.77,Default,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,What do you mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.13,0:13:51.83,Default,Panda,0,0,0,,I'm honestly not sure if it's good for SIRIUS
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.83,0:13:56.23,Default,Panda,0,0,0,,when the star of Aladdin is being \Nused as a foil for the Genie.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.10,0:14:00.17,Default,Panda,0,0,0,,Am I the only one worried about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.60,0:14:03.23,Default,Sasuga,0,0,0,,What's Shamo{**-san} saying about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.78,0:14:07.14,Default,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,I'm the one in charge of this production.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.07,0:14:11.30,Default,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,She's leaving everything to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.95,0:14:15.14,Default,Panda,0,0,0,,Then how do you feel about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.14,0:14:17.86,Default,Panda,0,0,0,,How do you feel about our current \Nproduction of {\i1}Arabian Nights{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.18,0:14:19.89,Default,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,How do {\i1}you{\i0} feel about it, Panda?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.80,0:14:23.06,Default,Panda,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.88,0:14:27.12,Default,Panda,0,0,0,,I honestly don't think it \Nrepresents SIRIUS at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.07,0:14:30.15,Default,Sasuga,0,0,0,,Panda...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.49,0:14:35.84,Default,Panda,0,0,0,,The reason you made Niizumacchi the \NGenie is to make her a Dai Star.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.28,0:14:39.78,Default,Panda,0,0,0,,I completely understand that \Nthis benefits SIRIUS.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.49,0:14:44.39,Default,Panda,0,0,0,,But if that's the only reason \Nyou decided to use Koko{**-chan},
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.39,0:14:46.39,Default,Panda,0,0,0,,I'm honestly disappointed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.99,0:14:48.34,Default,Panda,0,0,0,,Please excuse me.
