Dialogue: 1,0:15:11.84,0:15:13.22,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,A letter?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.23,0:15:18.20,Default,Niizuma,0,0,0,,{\i1}I have to go help out at a charity.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.60,0:15:22.49,Default,Niizuma,0,0,0,,{\i1}We don't have a show today, \Nso please get plenty of rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.10,0:15:23.94,Default,Niizuma,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yae.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.28,0:15:31.94,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,Shizuka{**-chan} still hasn't come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.07,0:15:38.80,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,Shizuka{**-chan}?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.48,0:15:43.66,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,Where are you, Shizuka{**-chan}?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.24,0:15:47.42,Default,Sasuga,0,0,0,,Coming...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.90,0:15:51.90,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,G-Good morning...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.90,0:15:53.00,Default,Sasuga,0,0,0,,Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.34,0:15:56.88,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,Um... Has Shizuka{**-chan} been by?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.88,0:15:58.34,Default,Sasuga,0,0,0,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.97,0:16:02.74,Default,Panda,0,0,0,,I actually haven't seen \NOshizu{**-chan} for a while now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.97,0:16:04.69,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.38,0:16:06.85,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,Th-Thanks.
